Stay 
 


After a day full of non-stop action in our casino, Blue Chip’s hotel offers the perfect place to relax. Whether you stay in our distinctive, 22-story Spa Blu Tower, or the Blue Chip Tower, you’ll enjoy a relaxation destination in one of our 486 luxurious rooms and suites. Complimentary Wi-Fi available in all guest rooms.		
