Play 







	   			Forget every casino you've ever visited. Prepare for something entirely different. And much better. We offer 65,000 square feet of gaming on a single luxurious and spacious level, with 42 table games, eight live poker room tables and more than 1,700 slots.  Open 24 hours a day, seven days a week, all year round.  With your favorite games – and the ultimate gaming environment– Blue Chip will put you in the mood to play.
		
