2 helpful votes 





“Nice Room Big Place”


Reviewed 1 week ago



via mobile




Everything was very nice at this hotel. The room was very big and everything was clean. However, I don't think I would stay here again unless I was specifically going to the casino. It is so big that it was cumbersome to get our things to the room. Also, because of the size it wasn't as cozy as many hotels. It is a nice place though.




Stayed July 2017, traveled as a couple



