Vincent C



Chicago





Level 6  Contributor 


118 reviews 


19 attraction reviews





32 helpful votes 





“Vegas Feel, Close to Home”


Reviewed 1 week ago



via mobile




This was my 1st trip here. We went to see a band where we knew the singer play in the band (South City Revival) that played in bar directly on your right when you walk into the casino. The music and drinks were a good start to a fun night. Very reasonable tables, plenty of machines as well. Our room was very nice, the bathroom had a spa feel to it. The rooms were also reasonably priced. Looking forward to coming back again.




Visited June 2017



