Neil CNiles, Michigan308Reviewed 2 weeks ago via mobile Nice Place to PlayNice hotels, restaurants, shops, but the casino is stingy. Fun place to spend a night or two. Just bring $$$. Restaurants range from reasonable to pricey, hotel rooms are nice, staff is friendly. Close to Lake Michigan and outlet mall.Thank Neil C 



