Never again
4/14/2006













1

Rebecca P.


                        My husband and I took an impromptu road trip and decided to check out the Blue Chip casino for a day. Never again will I go there. First of all, there was next to NO ventilation, so I felt like I was choking on cigarette smoke. Then they had slot machines shoved into every possible nook and cranny, so it made it nearly impossible to get around. The staff was rude and it just wasn't a fun time. Save your money and go to Windsor!
