Fun on Easy St.
12/18/2005













4

Mary R.


                        I absolutely love going to the Blue Chip or "The Boat."  I have never won much there but it is still fun to play. There is always an open seat at the tables or the slots. They recently added the penny slots. While they don't pay much their still fun. I wish they had lower limit blackjacks tables though. The restaurant has good food although the gift shop could be a little cheaper.
